# Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.

# --- Analytics (optional) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# --- Notes ---
# OpenSky API calls are made directly from the browser (CORS supported).
# No server-side credentials are needed.

# --- World Monitor Integration ---
# Airport delay intelligence is fetched server-side from the World Monitor
# aviation API (https://api.worldmonitor.app). No API key is required.
# The /api/airport-status route caches responses for 5 minutes.
# See: https://github.com/barbrickdesign/worldMonitor-enhancedByAgentR
